# ProgressBar

`TxProgressBar` covers known percentages, unknown-duration loading, success/error completion labels, segmented progress, tooltip labels, and optional motion effects.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/progress-bar/src/types.ts`, `TxProgressBar.vue`, and `progress-bar.test.ts`.

